th an aperiodic Haar regulaar window, and in Section 4 we\napply this fact to give an alternative proof of the finding \\cite{Mentzen2017}\nthat the centralizer of any $\\mathcal{B}$-free dynamical system of Erd\\\"os type\nis trivial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2016 09:52:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2016 19:53:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Oct 2017 06:17:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 15 May 2019 15:51:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-16"}
