t\ncalculation suggests the existence of the inversion doublets with the\n$^{24}$Mg+$\\alpha$, $^{16}$O+$^{12}$C and $^{20}$Ne+2$\\alpha$\nconfigurations.Because of the enhanced transition strengths, we offer the\nisoscalar monopole and dipole transitions as good probe for the\n$^{24}$Mg+$\\alpha$ and $^{20}$Ne+2$\\alpha$ cluster bands.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2016 09:58:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2016 00:44:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-03"}
